Class RevealingTxSystemClient.RevealingTransaction

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.tephra.Transaction
      • co.cask.cdap.test.RevealingTxSystemClient.RevealingTransaction
  • Enclosing class:
    RevealingTxSystemClient

    public static class RevealingTxSystemClient.RevealingTransaction
extends org.apache.tephra.Transaction
    This transaction class allows us to return additional details about the transaction to the client. For now, it is only the transaction timeout, but we can add more information later. This can then be used by test cases to validate that the transaction was started with the right properties.
